text: Tyrolean may refer to: * Anything from Tyrol (state) (Austria), South Tyrol (Italy) or the historical County of Tyrol or region of Tyrol * Tyrolean Zugspitze Cable Car * Tyrolean Airways * Tyrolean hat * Tyrolean traverse, mountaineering manoeuvre * Tyrolean Hound * A type of cement render, applied by a hand-operated machine
title: Tyrolean
